(186, 'Service', 'Deck Repair and Restoration - Service has been updated', 'App\\Models\\Service', 'updated', 42, NULL, NULL, '{\"attributes\":{\"id\":42,\"title\":\"Deck Repair and Restoration\",\"price\":150,\"video\":\"\",\"status\":1,\"duration\":\"3\",\"duration_unit\":\"minutes\",\"service_rate\":141,\"discount\":6,\"per_serviceman_commission\":8,\"description\":\"Our Deck Repair and Restoration service helps rejuvenate your existing deck, restoring its beauty and structural integrity. Whether your deck has suffered from weather damage, wear and tear, or simply needs a facelift, our skilled technicians provide comprehensive repair and restoration services, including sanding, staining, and structural repairs.\",\"content\":\"<p>If your deck has seen better days, it may be time for some professional attention. Our Deck Repair and Restoration services are designed to bring your deck back to life, improving both its appearance and functionality. We specialize in revitalizing worn, weathered, and damaged decks, restoring them to their original beauty.<\\/p> <p>Rather than spending money on replacing the entire deck, our repair and restoration services provide a more affordable solution to enhance its aesthetic and structural integrity. Whether it\\u00c3\\u0192\\u00c2\\u00a2\\u00c3\\u00a2\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0161\\u00c2\\u00ac\\u00c3\\u00a2\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u017e\\u00c2\\u00a2s cracked or faded boards, loose railings, or general wear and tear, we can handle it all.<\\/p> <p>Our Deck Repair and Restoration services include wood repair and replacement, where we replace damaged or rotted boards with high-quality materials that match the original look of your deck, ensuring a seamless finish. We also offer re-staining and refinishing, where we strip away old finishes, stains, and dirt, then apply fresh protective coatings to bring back the natural beauty of your deck and add a layer of protection from the elements. Additionally, we check the structural integrity of your deck 