(23, '{\"en\":\"Plumber Service\",\"ar\":\" \"}', 100.00, '{\"en\":null}', 1, '40', 'minutes', 90.00, 10.00, 8.00, '{\"en\":\"Our professional plumbers are available for all your plumbing needs, from installations to repairs. Whether it\'s a leaky faucet or a complete bathroom remodel, we\'ve got you covered.\",\"ar\":\"           .               .\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Plumber Service provides reliable and professional plumbing solutions for both residential and commercial needs. Whether you need a simple repair or a complete plumbing installation, our expert plumbers are ready to help you with any plumbing task.</p> <p>We offer a range of services to keep your plumbing in top shape. Our leak detection and repair service quickly identifies and fixes leaks, saving you from costly water damage. We also provide drain cleaning, ensuring your plumbing system remains free-flowing. If your pipes are old or worn-out, we can perform complete pipe replacements. Additionally, we offer fixture installations, including faucets, sinks, and toilets, done with precision and care.</p> <p>Our plumbers are licensed, insured, and experienced, handling all types of plumbing issues with ease. We pride ourselves on offering fast, reliable service, ensuring that your plumbing problems are resolved quickly. Plus, our pricing is competitive and transparent, ensuring that you get the best value for the services we provide.</p> <p>For any plumbing needs, contact our professional Plumber Service today. Were ready to help!</p>\",\"ar\":\"<p>           .                   .</p>\\r\\n<p>            .            .         .         .             .</p>\\r\\n<p>            .            .              .</p>\\r\\n<p>         .     !</p>\"}', '{\"ar\":null}', 23, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 1, 0, '1', '{\"ar\":null}', 'plumber-service', '{\"ar\":null}', 1, 0, 1, NULL, '2025-04-07 09:01:12', '2025-04-08 09:01:12', NULL),
(24, '{\"en\":\"AC Master Service\",\"ar\":\"  \"}', 60.00, '{\"en\":null}', 1, '3', 'hours', 57.00, 5.00, 7.00, '{\"en\":\"AC Master Service offers comprehensive air conditioning solutions, including installation, maintenance, cleaning, and repair. Our team of experienced technicians ensures your AC units operate efficiently and effectively, providing you with the comfort you need in your home or office. We pride ourselves on delivering prompt, professional, and reliable service to meet all your air conditioning needs.\",\"ar\":\"             .                      .            .\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our AC Master Service is designed to keep your air conditioning system running efficiently and effectively. With regular maintenance, your AC unit can last longer, perform better, and consume less energy. Trust us to ensure your system operates at peak performance.</p> <p>We offer a range of services to maintain your AC unit, including a comprehensive system check. Our team performs a full inspection of your AC system, checking the condenser, compressor, evaporator coil, and ductwork. We also replace air filters regularly, improving airflow and indoor air quality. Additionally, we check and replenish coolant levels to ensure your AC is cooling efficiently. To avoid unexpected breakdowns, we offer preventive maintenance plans that prepare your system for the warmer months.</p> <p>Our licensed HVAC technicians have years of experience in servicing and maintaining all types of air conditioning systems. Regular service helps prevent costly repairs and extends the lifespan of your AC unit, making it a cost-effective choice. We also offer flexible scheduling and personalized maintenance plans tailored to your specific needs.</p> <p>Ensure your air conditioning system runs smoothly all year round with our AC Master Service. Contact us to schedule your service today!</p>\",\"ar\":\"<p>   AC Master          .                  .        .</p>\\r\\n<p>               .               