(27, '{\"en\":\"Emergency Repair Service\",\"ar\":\"  \"}', 90.00, '{\"en\":null}', 1, '3', 'minutes', 83.70, 7.00, 6.00, '{\"en\":\"Emergency Repair Service provides fast and reliable repair solutions for urgent issues in your home or office. Our team of skilled technicians is available 24/7 to handle emergencies such as plumbing leaks, electrical failures, and HVAC malfunctions. We prioritize your safety and comfort, ensuring prompt and effective repairs to minimize any disruption to your daily routine.\",\"ar\":\"             .                      .                 .\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Emergency Repair Service is available to handle a wide range of urgent repairs for your home or business. Whether its a malfunctioning appliance, broken air conditioning, or faulty plumbing, we provide prompt and effective solutions to get things back to normal.</p> <p>We offer round-the-clock emergency repair services, so you never have to worry about being left in the lurch. From electrical issues to appliance malfunctions, we cover a variety of emergency repairs to meet your needs. Our team consists of trained professionals who can quickly assess and fix the issue with minimal disruption. We provide upfront pricing, ensuring that youre fully aware of the cost before any work begins.</p> <p>We understand the urgency of an emergency and provide quick service to minimize downtime. Our skilled team has the expertise to handle a variety of emergency repairs efficiently. Were committed to providing exceptional service and ensuring youre completely satisfied with our work.</p> <p>When you need urgent repairs, our Emergency Repair Service is here to help. Contact us now for fast, reliable service!</p>\",\"ar\":\"<p>              .                     .</p>\\r\\n<p>               .               .               .                .</p>\\r\\n<p>         .            .            .</p>\\r\\n<p>           .        !</p>\"}', '{\"ar\":null}', 3, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 1, 0, '2', '{\"ar\":null}