(28, '{\"en\":\"Plumbing Emergency Repair Service\"}', 60.00, NULL, 1, '3', 'minutes', 57.00, 5.00, 7.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Plumbing Emergency Repair Service offers immediate assistance for all urgent plumbing issues. Whether it\'s a burst pipe, a severe leak, or a clogged drain, our experienced plumbers are available around the clock to provide fast and effective repairs. We understand the importance of addressing plumbing emergencies promptly to prevent water damage and ensure the safety and comfort of your property.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Plumbing Emergency Repair Service is available 24\\/7 to handle any plumbing issues that arise unexpectedly. Whether it\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s a burst pipe, clogged drain, or leaking faucet, our experienced plumbers are ready to provide fast and reliable solutions to get your plumbing system back in working order.<\\/p> <p>We offer 24\\/7 emergency response, ensuring that no matter the time of day, we are available to address your plumbing emergency with quick, efficient service. Our team uses advanced tools to locate and repair leaks in your plumbing system, minimizing damage to your property. We also provide pipe repair and replacement services to keep your system running smoothly and without leaks. Additionally, our specialized equipment is used for drain cleaning, ensuring your drains flow freely.<\\/p> <p>Our plumbers are licensed and trained to handle all types of plumbing emergencies. We prioritize your plumbing emergency and work quickly to restore normal operation. We provide transparent pricing with no hidden fees, so you know exactly what to expect.<\\/p> <p>For any plumbing emergency, don\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122t hesitate to call our Plumbing Emergency Repair Service. We\'re here to help, 24\\/7!<\\/p>\"}', NULL, 3, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 1, 0, '1', NULL, 'plumbing-emergency-repair-service', NULL, 1, 0, 1, NULL, '2025-04-07 09:01:12', '2025-04-08 09:01:12', NULL),
(29, '{\"en\":\"Electrical Emergency Repair Service\"}', 90.00, NULL, 1, '3', 'minutes', 85.50, 5.00, 7.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Electrical Emergency Repair Service provides rapid response to urgent electrical issues. Whether you\'re dealing with power outages, faulty wiring, or electrical fires, our certified electricians are available 24\\/7 to address and resolve the problem. We ensure your electrical system is safe and functional, minimizing downtime and risk.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Electrical Emergency Repair Service is available 24\\/7 to handle any electrical issues that may arise in your home or business. From power outages and faulty wiring to electrical surges and circuit breaker problems, our licensed electricians are ready to resolve emergencies quickly and safely.<\\/p> <p>We are available around the clock to assist with any electrical emergency, ensuring your safety and comfort at all times. Our team responds promptly to all emergency service calls, arriving fully equipped to diagnose and fix the issue as quickly as possible. We also provide detailed inspections of your electrical system to identify potential hazards and ensure everything is up to code. Additionally, we offer repairs and replacements for circuit breaker issues, wiring malfunctions, and more to restore your electrical system\'s safety and functionality.<\\/p> <p>Our team is made up of licensed, highly trained professionals who have the expertise to handle all types of electrical emergencies. We prioritize emergency situations and work quickly to restore power and resolve any electrical issues efficiently. Your safety is our top priority, and we follow strict safety protocols to ensure the proper handling of all electrical repairs and installations.<\\/p> <p>Don\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122t let electrical problems disrupt your day. Contact our Electrical Emergency Repair Service anytime, and we\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122ll have your system back up and running safely and quickly!<\\/p>\"}', NULL, 33, NULL, 