(30, '{\"en\":\"Residential Cleaning Services\"}', 60.00, NULL, 1, '3', 'minutes', 57.00, 5.00, 5.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Home Cleaning Service provides thorough and detailed cleaning solutions for your entire home. Our professional cleaners use high-quality, eco-friendly products to ensure a clean and healthy living environment. From dusting and vacuuming to mopping and sanitizing, we cover every corner of your home to make it spotless.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Residential Cleaning Services are designed to keep your home spotless, organized, and healthy. Whether you need a one-time deep clean or regular cleaning services, our team delivers thorough, high-quality cleaning to make your living space feel fresh and inviting.<\\/p> <p>We offer routine cleaning, which includes dusting, vacuuming, mopping, and sanitizing surfaces in all areas of your home. For a more detailed service, we provide deep cleaning that goes beyond the surface, including baseboards, light fixtures, and hard-to-reach areas. We also offer move-in\\/move-out cleaning to ensure your new home is pristine or that your old home is ready for new tenants. Additionally, we use eco-friendly cleaning products that are safe for your family and pets, without compromising on effectiveness.<\\/p> <p>Our cleaning team is fully trained, insured, and background-checked, ensuring you receive top-quality service with peace of mind. We take the time to focus on the small details that make a big difference, leaving your home spotless and fresh. Our services are customizable to meet your specific needs, whether you require regular maintenance or a one-time deep cleaning.<\\/p> <p>Experience a clean, healthy, and organized home with our Residential Cleaning Services. Contact us today to schedule your cleaning appointment!<\\/p>\"}', NULL, 30, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 0, 0, '1', NULL, 'residential-cleaning-services', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2025-04-07 09:01:12', '2025-04-08 09:01:12', NULL),
(31, '{\"en\":\"Carpet Cleaning Service\"}', 30.00, NULL, 1, '2', 'minutes', 29.70, 1.00, 8.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Carpet Cleaning Service offers deep cleaning solutions to remove dirt, stains, and allergens from your carpets. Using advanced steam cleaning techniques and eco-friendly products, we ensure your carpets are fresh, clean, and extend their lifespan. Our experienced technicians handle all types of carpets and rugs with care.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our professional Carpet Cleaning Service helps you maintain clean and fresh carpets in your home or office. Using advanced cleaning methods, we remove deep dirt, stains, and allergens, leaving your carpets looking and feeling like new.<\\/p> <p>We offer deep cleaning using state-of-the-art equipment and eco-friendly solutions to eliminate stains, odors, and allergens. Our technicians are skilled at treating stubborn stains, ensuring that your carpets look as good as new. We also specialize in removing pet odors and stains, helping you maintain a fresh and healthy environment. Additionally, we use advanced techniques that ensure your carpets dry quickly, minimizing downtime.<\\/p> <p>We use safe, non-toxic cleaning solutions that are effective and gentle on your carpets and the environment. Our team is trained to handle all types of carpets and stains, delivering the best possible results. We guarantee that you\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122ll be satisfied with the results, or we\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122ll make it right.<\\/p> <p>Keep your carpets looking pristine with our Carpet Cleaning Service. Contact us today to schedule an appointment!<\\/p>\"}', NULL, 30, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 1, 0, '1', NULL, 'carpet-cleaning-service', NULL, 1, 0, 1, NULL, '2025-04-07 09:01:12', '2025-04-08 09:01:12', NULL),
(32, '{\"en\":\"Window Cleaning Service\"}', 200.00, NULL, 1, '1.5', 'minutes', 170.00, 15.00, 8.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Window Cleaning Service ensures your windows are crystal clear and streak-free. We provide both interior and exterior window cleaning using professional-grade equipment and techniques. Our trained staff will leave your windows spotless, improving the overall appearance and brightness of your home.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our professional Window Cleaning Service ensures that your windows are spotless, streak-free, and clear. We offer both residential and commercial window cleaning services to brighten your home or office with crystal-clear views.<\\/p> <p>We clean both the interior and exterior of your windows, ensuring every surface is free of dirt, dust, and streaks. In addition to the glass, we also clean the window screens and frames, leaving your entire window unit looking fresh. We use safe, eco-friendly cleaning solutions that are effective yet gentle on the environment. To maintain cleanliness year-round, we offer scheduled window cleaning services.<\\/p> <p>We don\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122t just clean the glass\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u201dwe take care of the frames and screens too, leaving every detail sparkling. Our team uses the latest tools and cleaning solutions to ensure the best results. We also provide flexible scheduling to ensure a hassle-free window cleaning experience that works around your needs.<\\/p> <p>Let us keep your windows sparkling with our Window Cleaning Service. Contact us today to schedule your cleaning appointment!<\\/p>\"}', NULL, 30, NULL, 'fixed', 0, 1, 0, '1', NULL, 'window-cleaning-service', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 09:01:12', '2025-04-08 09:01:12', NULL),
(33, '{\"en\":\"Custom Furniture Design and Build Furniture Making\",\"ar\":\"    \"}', 700.00, '{\"en\":null}', 1, '5', 'minutes', 665.00, 5.00, 8.00, '{\"en\":\"Our Custom Furniture Design and Build service offers personalized furniture solutions tailored to your specific needs and style preferences. Our skilled craftsmen work closely with you to create unique, high-quality pieces that perfectly fit your space and enhance your homes aesthetics. From concept to completion, we ensure every detail meets your expectations.\",\"ar\":\"                .                  .          .\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Our Custom Furniture Design and Build service allows you to create one-of-a-kind pieces that perfectly match your homes aesthetic. Whether you need a new dining table, bookshelf, or unique furniture piece, our expert craftsmen can bring your vision to life.</p> <p>We collaborate with you to design furniture that fits your space and style, from concept to creation. Each piece is meticulously built by our skilled artisans using high-quality materials to ensure longevity and functionality. You can choose from a wide range of materials, including wood, metal, glass, and fabric, to create furniture that suits your style and needs. Additionally, we offer on-site consultations to ensure that each piece is designed to fit perfectly in your home or office.</p> <p>Each piece we create is one-of-a-kind, ensuring that your furniture stands out and fits perfectly in your space. Our experienced craftsmen take great pride in every detail to deliver high-quality, durable furniture that youll cherish. We work closely with you throughout the entire design and building process, ensuring the final piece meets your exact specifications.</p> <p>Create bespoke furniture thats as unique as you are with our Custom Furniture Design and Build service. Contact us to begin designing your perfect piece.</p>\",\"ar\":\"<p>               .                    .</p>\\r\\n<p>          .                .    