rovince, ZIP\\/postal code, and city<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Information gathered through cookies and how you use our Service<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\\"list-item\\\">\\r\\n<h6>Usage Information<\\/h6>\\r\\n<p>We gather data on how you use our website, known as \\\"Usage Data.\\\" This includes:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Your computer\'s unique Internet Protocol (IP) address.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The type and version of your web browser.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Which pages of our website you visit.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The date and time of your visits.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>How long you spend on each page.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Unique identifiers for your device.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Other technical information we might need for diagnostics.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>This helps us understand how our website is used and improves your experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\\"list-item\\\">\\r\\n<h6>Tracking &amp; Cookies Data<\\/h6>\\r\\n<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to understand how you use our website.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Cookies are small files that store information about your browsing activity. They include an anonymous unique identifier and are stored on your device when you visit our website.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We use cookies, along with beacons, tags, and scripts, to gather and analyze information about your interactions with our website. This helps us improve and personalize your experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>You can choose to accept or reject cookies. However, if you reject them, some parts of our website may not work properly.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Examples of Cookies We Use:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li>Session Cookies: These are essential for the operation of our website.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Preference Cookies: These remember your preferences and settings.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Security Cookies: These help keep your information safe.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\"},{\"title\":\"2. How Your Information Is Used by Us\",\"description\":\"<ol class=\\\"list-items\\\">\\r\\